{"type": "article", "id": 16101, "title": "数字温度计", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-15T06:20:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 83, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150611GDMUduE9hAzWt8LJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冰冷的温度计常常让儿童感到害怕，几乎成为疾病的预示。而这根数字温度计贴在身上时不会造成太多感觉，它除了能直接看到温度外，还能连上手机 app 以读取最新的体温，直接对温度变化做一个详见的记录。对正在发烧的儿童来说非常实用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143459vqu89OtPfhZVx7MG.jpg\" width=\"951\" height=\"524\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55099895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143459DhC8bw1UgWPI5JGt.jpg\" width=\"525\" height=\"438\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143500dFR60HCyKqxuQXNl.jpg\" width=\"894\" height=\"624\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69798658\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143500DCrfVAZxIhmJPQTE.jpg\" width=\"606\" height=\"620\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.02310231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}